Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:22:01.19,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,How did they meet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:09.82,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Looking at such a lonely sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:17.33,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Even as I try to find clever words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:26.22,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,There are none to connect our distant hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:34.72,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Do you think if I wave with my best smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:43.35,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,That I might look even a little prettier?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:52.95,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,If I could have one wish granted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:23:01.58,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,It would be that our love wouldn't make us both hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,يا إلهي أهذا القدح الذي يساوي 10 مليون ين ؟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,مع أن منظره لا يوحي بذلك
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,لا تحكم على الشيئ من ظاهره
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.05,0:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,حار
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,أمزح
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:41.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,بالنسبة لعمي فإن باطنه لا يختلف عن ظاهره
