Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!  Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,still in there!
